WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:08.000
Finding care should not require understanding every part of the health system.

00:08.000 --> 00:16.000
But for many people, the hardest step is knowing where to begin.

00:16.000 --> 00:20.500
A service may exist. A licensed practitioner may be available.

00:20.500 --> 00:25.000
Yet the path between a person and that care may still be difficult to follow.

00:25.000 --> 00:31.000
SozoRock Health helps make that path clearer.

00:31.000 --> 00:36.500
We help people understand practical next steps, identify appropriate resources,

00:36.500 --> 00:42.000
and connect with licensed care where needed.

00:42.000 --> 00:46.000
We do not diagnose, treat, or prescribe.

00:46.000 --> 00:50.000
Licensed care stays with licensed professionals.

00:50.000 --> 00:56.500
Our work also helps communities, institutions, and public systems understand where access breaks down—

00:56.500 --> 01:01.000
and what can be done about it.

01:01.000 --> 01:06.000
Through research, partnerships, and practical implementation,

01:06.000 --> 01:10.000
SozoRock Health is working toward a simpler goal:

01:10.000 --> 01:17.000
A clearer path to care that already exists.

01:17.000 --> 01:20.000
SozoRock Health. An initiative of The SozoRock Foundation.
